The paper deals with image understanding, manipulation, and retrieval, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of shared embedding space and transfer learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The mention of synthesized 2D blobs image and 3D rendered image suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM), while the use of text domain for transformation transfer suggests a possible connection to natural language processing (cs.CL).
